!INC Local Scripts.EAConstants-VBScript
' ' Script Name: ' Author: ' Purpose: ' Date: ' sub tagPackageName(package, lang)
Session.Output "Tagging package " + package.name
'Define taggedValueName values dim labelName, prefLabelName, replaceExisting
labelName = "label " + lang prefLabelName = "prefLabel " + lang replaceExisting = true
'Tag package dim packageElement, packageName set packageElement = package.element packageName = packageElement.name setTaggedValue packageElement, labelName, stripName(packageName), replaceExisting, ""
'Tag children packages dim packages as EA.Collection set packages = package.packages dim x for x = 0 to packages.Count - 1 tagPackageName packages.GetAt(x), lang next
'Tag elements dim elements as EA.Collection dim element as EA.Element dim elementName set elements = package.elements
if elements.Count -1 > 0 then for x = 0 to elements.Count - 1 set element = elements.GetAt(x) elementName = element.Name setTaggedValue element, prefLabelName, stripName(elementName), replaceExisting, ""
'Tag attributes dim elementAttributes as EA.Collection dim attribute as EA.Attribute dim attributeName, j set elementAttributes = element.Attributes
if elementAttributes.Count - 1 > 0 then for j = 0 to elementAttributes.Count - 1 set attribute = elementAttributes.GetAt(j) attributeName = attribute.Name setTaggedValue attribute, prefLabelName, stripName(attributeName), replaceExisting, "" next end if
'Tag connectorEnds dim elementConnectors as EA.Collection dim connector as EA.Connector dim clientEnd as EA.Connector.ClientEnd dim supplierEnd as EA.Connector.SupplierEnd dim clientEndName, supplierEndName set elementConnectors = element.Connectors
if elementConnectors.Count - 1 > 0 then for j = 0 to elementConnectors.Count - 1 set connector = elementConnectors.GetAt(j) set clientEnd = connector.ClientEnd set supplierEnd = connector.SupplierEnd
if clientEnd.role <> "" then clientEndName = clientEnd.role setTaggedValue clientEnd, prefLabelName, stripName(clientEndName), replaceExisting end if
if supplierEnd.role <> "" then supplierEndName = supplierEnd.role setTaggedValue supplierEnd, prefLabelName, stripName(supplierEndName), replaceExisting end if
setTaggedValue attribute, prefLabelName, stripName(attributeName), replaceExisting, "" next end if next end if
end sub
sub setTaggedValue(obj, taggedValueName, taggedValueValue, replaceExisting, memoType)
'TODO IMPLEMENT THIS 'Session.Output "603 Object: " + obj.Name + ", tagName: " + taggedValueName + ", value: " + taggedValueValue + ", replace: " + CStr(replaceExisting) + ", isMemo: " + memoType
dim x
if not IsEmpty(obj) and taggedValueName <> "" then dim taggedValue as EA.TaggedValue taggedValue = null
dim objectTaggedValues as EA.Element.TaggedValues
Session.Output "THIS: " + TypeName(obj)
set objectTaggedValues = obj.TaggedValues
Session.Output "608: tagval count: " + CStr(objectTaggedValues.Count)
Session.Output "HERE: " + CStr(obj.objectType)
if obj.objectType = otConnectorEnd then for x = 0 to objectTaggedValues.Count - 1 if objectTaggedValues.GetAt(x).Tag = taggedValueName then if memoType <> "" then set taggedValue = objectTaggedValues.GetAt(x) set taggedValue.Value = "<memo>$ea_notes=" + taggedValueValue taggedValue.Update() obj.TaggedValues.Refresh() exit for else set taggedValue = objectTaggedValues.GetAt(x) set taggedValue.Value = taggedValueValue taggedValue.Update() obj.TaggedValues.Refresh() exit for end if end if next else for x = 0 to objectTaggedValues.Count - 1 'Session.Output "a:" + CStr(x) + ":" + CStr(obj) + ":" + CStr(obj.objectType) dim TagVa as EA.Element.TaggedValues set TagVA = obj.TaggedValues.GetAt(x) 'Session.Output "b" + x + ":" + obj.TaggedValues.GetLastError() 'Session.Output "#" + x + ":" + obj.TaggedValues.Count
Session.Output "name:" + TagVa.Name Session.Output " to be " + taggedValueName
if(obj.TaggedValues.GetAt(x).Name = taggedValueName) then if memoType <> "" then set taggedValue = objectTaggedValues.GetAt(x) taggedValue.Value = "<memo>" taggedValue.Notes = taggedValueValue taggedValue.Update() obj.TaggedValues.Refresh() exit for else set taggedValue = obj.TaggedValues.GetAt(x) taggedValue.Value = taggedValueValue taggedValue.Update() obj.TaggedValues.Refresh() exit for end if end if next end if if IsNull(taggedValue) or not replaceExisting then Session.Output "Adding new taggedValue. " + taggedValueName + ", " + taggedValueValue set taggedValue = obj.TaggedValues.AddNew(taggedValueName, taggedValueValue) taggedValue.Update() obj.TaggedValues.Refresh() end if end if end sub
function stripPrefix(objectName)
dim strString, strPattern, strReplace, strResult dim regExp
strPattern = "(^.*\:)"
Set regExp = New RegExp regExp.Pattern = strPattern
strResult = regExp.Replace(objectName, "")
stripPrefix = strResult
end function
function stripName(value)
dim strString, strPattern, strReplace, strResult dim regExp dim result
strPattern = "([a-z])([A-Z])/g"
strReplace = "$1 $2"
Set regExp = New RegExp regExp.Pattern = strPattern
result = stripPrefix(value)
stripName = regExp.Replace(result, strReplace)
end function
function synchronizePackage(projectInterface, package) dim packageGUIDXML packageGUIDXML = projectInterface.GUIDtoXML(package.packageGUID) projectInterface.SynchronizePackage packageGUIDXML, "children=1" end function
